show.description: Anushka’s perfect life shatters after betrayal, heartbreak, and a tragic loss—until a mysterious, seductive gigolo named Reyansh turns her world upside down. But what happens when she discovers he’s not who he says he is? Dive into a gripping tale of revenge, romance, and buried secrets. Watch Now !
